dct_title_s: State of New Jersey, Board of Commerce and Navigation, map showing riparian conveyances in the vicinity of Fort Lee Pier South
dct_description_sm: Map showing property lines, indicating grantors and lessees along the Hudson River in Edgewater, Fort Lee, and the area formerly known as Pettigrew's Quarries
Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
Map contains details about property records (in terms of Liber) as well as real estate prices per foot.
